here,i have done a js file named main.js

start the node server

port is 3000

1)use the html file enter_n.htm

give the input value n

 In a blog, get the author info of n'th post from the latest. (input: n)
API : https://public-api.wordpress.com/rest/v1.1/sites/discover.wordpress.com/posts/

2. goto localhost:3000/tags

Get the tags statistics of posts he has written. (Count the occurences of tags in his posts)
API : https://public-api.wordpress.com/rest/v1.1/sites/discover.wordpress.com/posts/?author={ID}

3.  goto localhost:3000/tag_posts

Get the latest post for the tag having maximum occurrence. (Return a post that is written by other author and not by the selected author)
API : https://public-api.wordpress.com/rest/v1.1/sites/discover.wordpress.com/posts/?tag={tag_slug}
